high_descs: Turn right then face the table with the coffee machine on your left.
Take the cup from the coffee machine in front of you.
Turn left then face the microwave to your right.
Heat up the cup in the microwave then take it out.
Turn left then face the microwave to your right.
Place the cup by the microwave in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a hot cup of coffee near the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right, turn left at the stove to face the counter with the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug from the coffee maker.
Turn left and walk to the microwave to the right of the fridge.
Open the microwave door, place the mug inside of the microwave, heat the mug, take the mug out of the microwave, close the door.
Move to the counter space to the left of the microwave.
Put the mug down on the counter behind the pepper mill.
anns.task_desc: To heat a mug and put it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and then left to face the counter with the coffee maker on it.
Pick the mug up from under the coffee maker.
Go left and then turn the right to face the microwave.
Put the mug in the microwave and shut the door and then open the door and pick the mug up again.
Back up and move to the left side of the microwave.
Put the mug down in front of a microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug down on the counter in front of a microwave.
